link(rel='stylesheet', href='css/login.css')

.col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.col-xs-12
    .row
        .col-md-12.col-xs-12
            .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3.text-center
                h3 Create your online contact URL
                h4 www.mpeers.com/you
    .row
        .col-md-12.col-xs-12
            .row
                hr
                .col-md-7.col-xs-12.jumbotron
                    ul
                        li Create your online contact point.
                        li Share it online.
                        li Others can "click and chat" with you.
                .col-md-4.col-xs-10.content-box(style='background: #eeeeee;')
                    .row
                        .col-md-12.col-xs-12.heading-banner.text-center
                            label Sign In
                    .row
                        .col-md-12.col-xs-12.text-center(style='padding: 5px; margin-top: 10px;')
                            form.form-horizontal
                                .col-md-12(style='margin-bottom: 10px;')
                                    input(class="form-control", type="text", id="userNameLogin", placeholder="UserName", ng-model='userLogin.username')
                                .col-md-12(style='margin-bottom: 10px;')
                                    input(class="form-control", type="password", id="inputPasswordLogin", placeholder="Password", ng-model='userLogin.password')
                                .col-md-12
                                    .btn.btn-primary(type='submit', ng-click='logUserIn(userLogin)', style='margin-right: 5px;') Sign in
                                    label or
                                    .btn.btn-success(type='submit', ng-click='', style='margin-left: 5px;') Sign up


            .row
                h4 Who can use it
                hr
                .col-md-3.col-xs-8.content-box.pull-left(style='height: 300px;')
                    .row
                        .col-md-12.heading-banner.text-center
                            label Service providers
                    .row.text-center
                        img(src='/img/service.png', style='height: 80px; width: 80px;')
                    .row
                        .col-md-12.text-center
                            h4 Customers or prospective customers can chat with you without the hasle of signing up for a service or sharing their personnel info.
                .col-md-3.col-xs-8.content-box.pull-left(style='height: 300px;')
                    .row
                        .col-md-12.heading-banner.text-center
                            label Events
                    .row.text-center
                        img(src='/img/calendar.png', style='height: 80px; width: 80px;')
                    .row
                        .col-md-12.text-center
                            h4 Participants and guests can stay connected with the event organisers.
                .col-md-3.col-xs-8.content-box.pull-left(style='height: 300px;')
                    .row
                        .col-md-12.heading-banner.text-center
                            label Individual
                    .row.text-center
                        img(src='/img/people.png', style='height: 80px; width: 80px;')
                    .row
                        .col-md-12.text-center
                            h4 You can share the URL on websites, blogs, social networks, resumes etc. and be reachable for a chat.


